| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2117 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6a16e0dc-cfbc-5cd4-9c10-e85f1228929a"
